latestIgtvVideos.title: My vote out!!!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The only time i did not want @rannvijaysingha sir to take my name!! As i was walking towards him with a heavy heart, this was a very very sad moment for me! I did not know then who voted against me! Saw that yesterday and could not stop thinking for even once that what went wrong!! 
Atleast apoorva was clear that she wanted to shine what was my friend’s excuse?? Lol 
I made really really good friends too! 
Starting with @akashmilan_sher , @abhimanyuraghav2 , @iamsupertaran , @srishti_sudhera , @aman07aman ! 
You made my stay memorable ❤️❤️❤️
And yes i wanted to win roadies too but  playing it without my friends made no sense to me 😅 life should not always be about winning, it should be about living too! And i lived my journey, had so much of fun! 
I hope i made you guys smile 😃❤️
